title: Lily Allen covers (covers by Lily Allen)
description:
Six covers by Lily Allen

Covers - Oh My God (Kaiser Chiefs), Heart Of Glass (Blondie), Naive (Kooks), Straight To Hell (The Clash), Gangsters (The Specials), Blank Expression (The Specials).

Straight To Hell is off of War Child Heroes, an album of classic covers by modern stars.

The two Specials covers are also known as The Ska EP, also available her,e the same exact files - http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/7183124/
